Description: DuckBotOS Hermes agent mode — primary AI-first desktop
 Installs Hermes as the primary desktop agent for DuckBotOS.
 Hermes boots as a fullscreen shell replacing the traditional desktop,
 providing an AI-native interaction layer built on a natural language
 package manager, predictive resource orchestration, and multi-provider
 LLM support.
 .
 Installs hermesos-agent package from pip (hermesai/hermes-os).
 Includes hermes-nlpkg (natural language package manager).
 Includes hermesos-watchdog (predictive resource orchestrator daemon).
 .
 Port 8000: OpenAI-compatible REST API for Hermes tools
 Port 8001: Hermes agent bus (Unix socket IPC for OpenClaw coordination)
 Port 8002: Hermes NLP package manager bus
 .
 Weston kiosk launches hermesos-agent on login.
 GDM session "DuckBotOS Hermes" boots directly to Hermes dashboard.
